9s behaviors began to change. He stopped having emotional breakdowns. His aggressive, defiant behaviors changed.<\/p>\n<p>Like Matthew, each child we care for comes to us broken and bruised from trauma inflicted by the people they love the most.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Be the hope. And help the Home.\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Because kids like Matthew don\u2019t need secrets. \u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.homeoftheinnocents.org\/donate-now\/\"><strong>Make a contribution today!<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1958\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/www.homeoftheinnocents.org\/app\/uploads\/2017\/05\/992093-1.jpg?resize=289%2C207\" alt=\"Purchase this image at https:\/\/www.stocksy.com\/992093\" width=\"289\" height=\"207\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/www.homeoftheinnocents.org\/app\/uploads\/2017\/05\/992093-1.jpg?resize=300%2C215&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/www.homeoftheinnocents.org\/app\/uploads\/2017\/05\/992093-1.jpg?w=520&amp;ssl=1 520w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 289px) 100vw, 289px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Matthew has a secret. He hides it underneath the long sleeve shirts he wears. He hides it when he can\u2019t make eye contact with strangers. He hides it behind the words he shouts when he feels threatened. Matthew thinks his secret means no one can love him. When Matthew came to Home of the Innocents,<a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.homeoftheinnocents.org\/be-the-hope\/\">&#8230;Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"spay_email":"","jetpack_publicize_message":"","jetpack_is_tweetstorm":false},"categories":[11],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_publicize_connections":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v15.3 - https:\